/*
 * Author: Belbo
 *
 * Fills a crate with ammunition for roughly a fire team for OPFOR
 *
 * Arguments:
 * Array of objects - <ARRAY> of <OBJECTS>
 *
 * Return Value:
 * Function executed - <BOOL>
